@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mfcozb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.22) - (v2 + 0.95 + v2 + 0.48)) - ((v0 + 0.44 + v2 + 0.20) + (v1 + 0.37 - v1 + 0.32)))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.95)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.90)) / (wp.sin(v2 + 0.17) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.88)))
    v0 = wp.abs((v0 + (v0 + 0.08 + tmp + 0.91)))
    data[tid] = v0
